{"tid":1316963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(集思廣益) 新城市廣場抵制行動","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T17:35:51.000Z","uid":65611,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d301b79752e43cb5ecbf05dc26c0d86b5abf5bca","tid":1316963,"uid":65611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:07:41.000Z","msg":"首先，商場入面主要有三大部門，租務部、市場推廣部同埋物業管理部(姐係清潔，停車場，保安，控制商場秩序人流咁樣)。<br />\n<br />\n今次班黑警可以入到商場一定係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">物業管理部</span></strong>嗰班呀頭放佢地入去，佢地先可以入到。<br />\n<br />\n唔好再信話咩商場單方面講佢地冇俾防暴入場，如果係咁，點解上次太古廣場班狗又入唔到pp呢？<br />\n<br />\n咁好明顯今次係有人放犬入去。<br />\n<br />\n所以呢大家可以好好諗下點樣抵制返佢地，特別係今次放到班犬入商場係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">物業管理部</span></strong>嘅決定。<br />\n<br />\n咁作為沙田區龍頭商場，當然係有好多元化嘅服務提供到俾顧客，例如下面就係新城市現有嘅服務，我相信顧客有咩要求新城市都幫到佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3F9qdf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3F9qdf3.jpg&h=d57a12dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jv86G9n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJv86G9n.jpg&h=354e2397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(以上服務好大機會都適用於其他新鴻基商場)<br />\n<br />\n至於其他方面交返俾連登各位巴打出招 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786f80f4b6ba5e6d65befd9d760c8b4770629b11","tid":1316963,"uid":255127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:19:59.000Z","msg":"聽朝打去客服嘈9佢"},{"pid":"d9fff503db3268a55d029dca71db8fbe345f3f8a","tid":1316963,"uid":65611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"786f80f4b6ba5e6d65befd9d760c8b4770629b11","tid":1316963,"uid":255127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:19:59.000Z","msg":"聽朝打去客服嘈9佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:20:57.000Z","msg":"我要投訴"},{"pid":"f863973793e95d5a5b13416d27d0580563c9b410","tid":1316963,"uid":129243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e640f992106454b0a17213e598723128d1a484","tid":1316963,"uid":65611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9fff503db3268a55d029dca71db8fbe345f3f8a","tid":1316963,"uid":65611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"786f80f4b6ba5e6d65befd9d760c8b4770629b11","tid":1316963,"uid":255127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:19:59.000Z","msg":"聽朝打去客服嘈9佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:20:57.000Z","msg":"我要投訴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:23:32.000Z","msg":"寫email 叫佢地物管覆<br />\n<br />\n商場物管最睇重有冇準時覆客嘅查詢，有冇follow up客嘅投訴，如果係咁投訴佢地呢樣嗰樣佢地物管應該會做到狗咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae10d1bdf66c97bef1e7190636e33c68434995c","tid":1316963,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:25:16.000Z","msg":"建議秋後啦<br />\n而家眼前係打好輿論<br />\n仲有黑警五大訴求"},{"pid":"3e25118641b830cea0d4ce225e70b8b94f139e26","tid":1316963,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:26:33.000Z","msg":"文宣攻保皇：前線警中矢之的，偽建制派議員全部失蹤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316637</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79e280092c8d4c3354516fc227e1f979bcbbcb18","tid":1316963,"uid":113937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:35:51.000Z","msg":"唔係想掃興<br />\n但係新城市大陸人消費多 淨係我地唔買應該對佢哋得少少影響<br />\n會唔會有辦法令d蝗都唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}